{"tid":25381,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇行過香港?","createTime":"2016-12-06T05:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T15:28:02.000Z","uid":53440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae33c230d160ca0bba3ea6c0884f90a7a92c42bd","tid":25381,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得身為香港人應該要欣賞下香港<br />\n香港做得旅遊熱點<br />\n咁自然有佢既景點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有冇咩推介???<br />\n行山睇景 旅遊景點個d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先比一個最普通既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n龍脊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攝自S7<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRY4pjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRY4pjH.jpg&h=1a3c02c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其實我係黎乞地方</span>"},{"pid":"bc8a6418042cac24040281a33946aeff8f8d791b","tid":25381,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"重慶大廈"},{"pid":"9e3b287c67c9ecb88ca3047bda1a892c17bd6f1f","tid":25381,"uid":37651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山昂平,第一次去坐係山坡兩個鐘唔捨得行"},{"pid":"ae49e67ba1fc0c96a9c3c488722ce3cc9773e801","tid":25381,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>馬鞍山昂平,第一次去坐係山坡兩個鐘唔捨得行</blockquote><br />\n遲啲行下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1f0f213dccec986941d11a9d42878fbeef7ae4","tid":25381,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"獅子山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望落去九龍好靚"},{"pid":"442fcb9eb3e935a2ec75b195676b96f7f54ec67e","tid":25381,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"大帽山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774dce8ae226595689a19a199709cd192cb4ac8a","tid":25381,"uid":464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:32:07.000Z","msg":"其實市區後面果排山已經好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望番落黎既夜景真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己都係行啲大路既山，大東山 獅子山 浪茄呢啲<br />\n係去過蚺蛇尖同釣魚翁已經覺得夠皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日出都有睇過幾個地方，飛鵝山 大帽山 鶴咀 東壩<br />\n天清既時候我覺得鶴咀係最靚，不過果到有車先好去啦盡量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有幸見識過一次大帽山雲海日出，我果日已經唔算最靚，但係已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東壩日出就係睇流星睇埋既<br />\n龍脊呢期俾人吹奏緊實多人琴旺角咁，暫時未去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面講馬鞍山昂坪我都好想去<br />\n去過就會郊野公園真係香港既寶黎，唔好拆佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd530b3a08574c2a70a67e90c873167fe209e81","tid":25381,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實市區後面果排山已經好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望番落黎既夜景真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己都係行啲大路既山，大東山 獅子山 浪茄呢啲<br />\n係去過蚺蛇尖同釣魚翁已經覺得夠皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日出都有睇過幾個地方，飛鵝山 大帽山 鶴咀 東壩<br />\n天清既時候我覺得鶴咀係最靚，不過果到有車先好去啦盡量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都有幸見識過一次大帽山雲海日出，我果日已經唔算最靚，但係已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東壩日出就係睇流星睇埋既<br />\n龍脊呢期俾人吹奏緊實多人琴旺角咁，暫時未去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面講馬鞍山昂坪我都好想去<br />\n去過就會郊野公園真係香港既寶黎，唔好拆佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鶴咀 勁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋英文名好浪漫"},{"pid":"8c932b040f61ea79bdb9bdca87049d8a7cb3ec23","tid":25381,"uid":2193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/000404_62e36e2534cb745054b0b70786d8444f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F000404_62e36e2534cb745054b0b70786d8444f.jpg&h=b2c1f728&s={SIZE}\" /><del></del><ins></ins><br />\n龍脊真心靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb268e16a9684438a6025419a8b10b3b7033843","tid":25381,"uid":2014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"釣魚翁我行過咁多山覺得最靚 可能有海既關係 但一定要好好陽光先得"},{"pid":"35b2736efd7e016037d36146a6a05b233f3ccfd2","tid":25381,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/000404_62e36e2534cb745054b0b70786d8444f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F000404_62e36e2534cb745054b0b70786d8444f.jpg&h=b2c1f728&s={SIZE}\" /><del></del><em></em><br />\n龍脊真心靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n相比樓豬嗰張，我欣賞佢啲色多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6daea5708917647f725dcf70ed70d92c9219425","tid":25381,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T18:15:27.000Z","msg":"有無人鍾意行舊區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d57b7ef13fe8d5b4cedaffc812bbe0ee6a9a591","tid":25381,"uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人鍾意行舊區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\